 SB_DEBUG
     Format:-SB_DEBUG [TRUE|FALSE]
      Modes:-DPM, REP, SFN
    Description:- When TRUE, SCHUR results are shown with some intermediate
	(ugly) results to help on debugging the code. Use with caution,
	since it can be very verbose. The default value is set as FALSE.

NOTES:	few commands are concerned by this debugging actually.
